{"tid":771933,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登力學/航空科技","createTime":"2018-08-08T11:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T12:40:05.000Z","uid":142854,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab8e6666e8aea90ea395bb9ef9fcb8ec615769ef","tid":771933,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"其實至古以黎古代人發明過好多關於力學既定理<br />\n經過幾千年 萊特兄弟最後征服到飛行呢個難題<br />\n但其實有冇可能將現時所發現既力學更加廣泛應用係生活之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係幾個倒子<br />\n<br />\n1. 以極高速左腳踏右腳,右腳踏左腳,不斷重復,直至飛行<br />\n<br />\n2. 在升降機墜落時，算準升降機碰撞地面前一刻立即跳起<br />\n<br />\n3. 搖搖板雙人飛行<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/190224_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F190224_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=dd14364c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾類野有冇可能應用係現代航空學到<br />\n使用 1 黎升高 , 之後用3黎製造雙人飛行 , 再使用2黎著陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8856fa6a1f3b1261a38b9252be9491139cafc432","tid":771933,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab8e6666e8aea90ea395bb9ef9fcb8ec615769ef","tid":771933,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"其實至古以黎古代人發明過好多關於力學既定理<br />\n經過幾千年 萊特兄弟最後征服到飛行呢個難題<br />\n但其實有冇可能將現時所發現既力學更加廣泛應用係生活之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係幾個倒子<br />\n<br />\n1. 以極高速左腳踏右腳,右腳踏左腳,不斷重復,直至飛行<br />\n<br />\n2. 在升降機墜落時，算準升降機碰撞地面前一刻立即跳起<br />\n<br />\n3. 搖搖板雙人飛行<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/190224_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F190224_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=dd14364c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾類野有冇可能應用係現代航空學到<br />\n使用 1 黎升高 , 之後用3黎製造雙人飛行 , 再使用2黎著陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a42b51446d3f65c845bf690c7825a1e7b7213c","tid":771933,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"留低負評唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n係child登到討論物理都估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d020fb7177409d8070ee86907b3aea1f8a8fe42","tid":771933,"uid":195030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:22:53.000Z","msg":"升到高中學少少物理就會明架啦，唔洗咁急，專心讀小學課程先啦"},{"pid":"5aec31396ae92b0eb293701f8d2e723d023da5b3","tid":771933,"uid":36868,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"84a42b51446d3f65c845bf690c7825a1e7b7213c","tid":771933,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"留低負評唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n係child登到討論物理都估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:23:57.000Z","msg":"你連最基本物理知識都冇討論乜鳩<br />\n多鳩餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77f8ebe0a60a87908518373371003c5d3cd6d5d","tid":771933,"uid":142854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5aec31396ae92b0eb293701f8d2e723d023da5b3","tid":771933,"uid":36868,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"84a42b51446d3f65c845bf690c7825a1e7b7213c","tid":771933,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"留低負評唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n係child登到討論物理都估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:23:57.000Z","msg":"你連最基本物理知識都冇討論乜鳩<br />\n多鳩餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:25:38.000Z",